snippet.title: Need for Speed Rivals Trailer - Cops vs Racers (Official E3 2013)
snippet.description:
Need for Speed Rivals releases 11.19.13 | The Rivalry Begins http://bit.ly/11uEMsb
This is the first trailer presented at the 2013 EA E3 Press Conference. Need for Speed Rivals is available for pre-order now on Xbox One, PS4, Xbox 360, PS3 & PC.

Like us on Facebook: http://on.fb.me/11p7cDS
